{"tid":2397404,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有留意三文魚aqb 又有無人留意牛油果avo","createTime":"2021-02-06T11:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T13:10:49.000Z","uid":137966,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17e56e37f12ec6678dcb09620a0ca9960f610fab","tid":2397404,"uid":137966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"Mission Produce是全球最大的牛油果公司。目前Mission Produce已經成為一傢俱有生產、供應和營銷的國際化運營公司及牛油果供應商，擁有在美國、墨西哥、新西蘭、智利和祕魯等9個不同國家的牛油果種植園。2018年3月，Mission Produce在上海建成催熟中心，向中國消費者提供成熟的牛油果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sz1yrDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSz1yrDa.jpg&h=e91ff1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n招股書顯示，Mission Produce截至2019年10月31日止的財年營收為8.83億美元，上年同期的營收為8.6億美元；Mission Produce在2020年7月31日止的9個月營收為6.56億美元，上年同期營收為6.52億美元。Mission Produce此次一共發行9,375,000股，其中，公司出售6,250,000股，現有股東出售3,125,000股。其發行區間為15美元到17美元，預估市值11.1億美元，募資額1.5億美元，公司可獲得資金約1億美元，現有股東可套現約5000萬美元。"},{"pid":"214e161819334c975edaa22d864db684b060d6e2","tid":2397404,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"牛油果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dfb7b6d5872b1b863610108a342cc1e5f89ce1","tid":2397404,"uid":44198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"牛油果好撚戇鳩喎，成日開左先知未食得/壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dde62227a7359e6d3675a4c7472eb46a72ca23","tid":2397404,"uid":21872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T13:10:49.000Z","msg":"三文魚多咁多on9港女食 決定買三文魚"}]}